--- !u!114 &8943850837050227469
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 6446001551011754798}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0f939d5fcafb87a49902064df3aa78d0, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  attacks:
  - attack: {fileID: 2943250936750891850}
    randomChance: 5
  - attack: {fileID: 5279885802054186098}
    randomChance: 2
  - attack: {fileID: 2356007468357865712}
    randomChance: 2
  attackCooldown: 3
  spriteRenderer: {fileID: 1226900822997898304}
  miniBoss: 0
  SecondPhase: 0
  _player: {fileID: 0}
  attackCooldownTimer: 0
  grounded: 0
  bounceOffWall: 1
  faceTowardPlayer: 1
  hardMode: 0
  Dialogue:
  - "\u2026Oh. You\u2019re just standing there. Staring. That\u2019s\u2026 comforting."
  - "Listen, if you\u2019re here for eggs, they\u2019re over there. If you\u2019re
    here for trouble, I\u2019m off duty."
  - "Still nothing? Wow. Intense. You\u2019ve got the energy of someone who lost
    an egg in 2011 and never emotionally recovered."
  - "Okay, okay\u2014don\u2019t look at me like that. I\u2019ll move the eggs next
    year. Maybe."
  - "Are you\u2026 are you trying to fight me? Because I should warn you, I do cardio
    all year. Hopping is basically CrossFit."
  - "\u2026Right. Silent type. Mysterious. I respect it. Terrifies me, but I respect
    it."
  - "Fine. Take the chocolate. Just stop looming. You\u2019re stressing out a seasonal
    icon."
  RepeatDialogue:
  - Back again to challenge the mighty Easter Bunny once more? you already lost (attempt_count)
    times.
  - 'I see you''re back, do you want a reminder to never fight the mighty Easter
    Bunny. I will make your attempts:  (attempt_count)  turn to infinity.'
  - I'm getting board killing you can we just end this fast, like all other fights.
    You have already lost around (attempt_count) times. Lets just end this fast.
  dialogueTypingSpeed: 0.02
  DialogueImage: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueTxt: {fileID: 0}
  trueDialogueTypingSpeed: 0
  DontDoDialouge: 1
